{"tid":942341,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人BB嘅年紀已經開始學英文 但係點解香港人嘅母語唔係廣東話同英文","createTime":"2018-12-15T15:21:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T02:37:04.000Z","uid":47857,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e48c0ffaaec49a500d600df84fcafdb70a16f703","tid":942341,"uid":47857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T15:21:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/母語\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E6%AF%8D%E8%AA%9E&d=KaGLeCdS41xqPAjz77DAE%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=8d7a6323\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/母語</a><br />\n<code>母語，又稱第一語言，為一個人出生以後，最早接觸、學習、並掌握的一種或幾種語言。母語一般是自幼即開始接觸、並持續運用到青少年或之後；並且，一個人所受的家庭或正式教育中，尤其是早期，有相當部分是通過母語傳授的。一個人同時可以擁有多種母語，並且可以使用雙語或多種語言。</code><br />\n<br />\n依家好多幼稚園 playgroup 甚至屋企老竇老母都已經同班BB(唔計支那腥移民雙飛)講英文教英文<br />\n而且中小學亦都有教學生英文 所以符合咗持續運用至青少年或之後嘅定義<br />\n但係點解冇人會話英文係同廣東話並列做母語 而剩係將廣東話列做香港人嘅母語呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a506f0ddb78a7b226283daec0189a797c69da1a6","tid":942341,"uid":62294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T15:30:11.000Z","msg":"大把人唔識啦"},{"pid":"5afdbc3cc7b5993935680363f8a03d67fa9a5c29","tid":942341,"uid":62294,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T15:30:22.000Z","msg":"問下含大學生先"},{"pid":"bf2d331875a897d2b0cdbac0153d948fc4166d23","tid":942341,"uid":78429,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T15:34:25.000Z","msg":"屋企老竇老母講嗰啲有時真係聽到毛管戙"},{"pid":"44ab193bf7e1296d49b34c2d7df4571b916caba9","tid":942341,"uid":112551,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T17:27:41.000Z","msg":"無聽過有人講母語講到錯晒grammar"},{"pid":"5de23d33f3d3de3cbc594bb7b4b131119a82aa4f","tid":942341,"uid":11598,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T17:31:57.000Z","msg":"come here 啦，食嘢喇<br />\n喂！dirty呀，dont touch!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286caf36db22a8c67cc0dde919e4fed8a0ecfd6f","tid":942341,"uid":192734,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T17:49:58.000Z","msg":"真正bilingual既人少之又少<br />\n一般香港細路無辦法喺日常自然環境習得英文<br />\n刻意製造出離的既學習就已經係第二語言學習<br />\n香港可以有bilingual既小朋友 但係唔多<br />\n就算讀國際學校令你英文變母語<br />\n但你又同時好難學好中文<br />\n就好似學輸入法 就算識兩種都會偏愛其中一款"},{"pid":"c5722a69e67f3b96947be792b90cc4c93e1141a3","tid":942341,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T18:31:06.000Z","msg":"因為出街d人都係講粵語"},{"pid":"02f1014fa19ec714ef0c9afc6e3b8901cee6bfe3","tid":942341,"uid":44391,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T18:38:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c487ffb4339ba002307b82b210d3dd11f3d11846","tid":942341,"uid":224916,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T23:09:13.000Z","msg":"你叫返從政班人開會用全英，然後新聞報佢地係垃圾會嘈交果陣都係全英嘈，你信我，香港人英文能力會升得好快<br />\n<br />\n因為同人互屌係學語言一大要點"},{"pid":"2f369e11e9c3913f17b45244e1e09da020bd78d5","tid":942341,"uid":42283,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T23:11:54.000Z","msg":"香港人母語係睇你屋企有幾多錢"},{"pid":"53408c481ab46b4d23efc8445a67df9491f99a1f","tid":942341,"uid":5384,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"5de23d33f3d3de3cbc594bb7b4b131119a82aa4f","tid":942341,"uid":11598,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T17:31:57.000Z","msg":"come here 啦，食嘢喇<br />\n喂！dirty呀，dont touch!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T23:33:46.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n喺地鐵車廂聽唔少呢啲家長係咁講嘢<br />\n好心一係就全英一係就全中啦<br />\n又講唔撚到一句完整英文就咪撚咁格硬嚟啦<br />\n中英夾雜做壞手勢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08cef29dc4ac9567104da9b241964d87